window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The most important magical creature has gone missing, and it’s up to Warrior Liv Beaufont to find him. But she has no idea where to look. </b></p> <p>Thankfully she’s made friends in lots of places - big and small. Liv pulls all her resources together to complete the most important mission she’s ever attempted. </p> <p>The House bonds together unlike ever before, and the timing couldn’t be any better as Talon Sinclair steps out of the Black Void to take control, once and for all. </p> <p>Liv will die before she allows the God Magician to ruin the world she loves so much. She just hopes it actually doesn’t kill her...or anyone she loves.</p>"; 
